quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"Mi laЙ“Й“inaa hoore-am, tawde wonkii ko heewuki yamirde bone, si wanah kin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  12,54,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: \"Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am\". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: \"An on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku hoolaaЙ—o"
  12,55,"O maaki: \"WaЙ—am e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi reenoowo annduЙ—o"
  12,56,"Ko wano nii Men Г±imnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, himo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yiЙ—i. MeЙ—en heЙ“nira yurmeende Amen nden on mo Men muuyi, men yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖґЖґinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,57,Pellet ko njoЙ“di laakara ndin Й“uri moЖґЖґannde Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e laatii gomЙ—uЙ“e
  12,58,"Baaba-gootooЙ“e Yuusufa Й“en ari Й“e naati ka makko. O annditi Й“e, kono kamЙ“e Й“e paayti mo"
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannooЙ“e doЕ‹lle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o maaki: \"Addanee lam musiЙ—Й—o mon baaba-gooto. E on yi'aali miЙ—o timmina Й“etu ngun, e wonnde ko mi Й“urdo moЖґЖґude e weernooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray Й“etu alanaa on ka am Й—oo; wata on Й“ado lam kadi"
  12,61,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"Men Й—aЙ“Й“iray mo ben makko, menen ko men gollooЙ“e (Й—um)"
  12,62,"O maakani gollooЙ“e makko Й“en: \"WaЙ—ee coggeeli(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka doЕ‹lle maЙ“Й“e: belajo'o Й“e annditay Й—i si Й“e ruttike ka yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e yiltoto"
  12,63,"Tuma nde Й“e ruttinoo ka ben maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben(baaba) amen, men salanaama Й“etu. neldu amen musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“etanee. Ko men reenooЙ“e mo"
  12,64,"O maaki: \"Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo on non e neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni moЖґЖґo reenoowo, ko Kanko Й“uri moЖґЖґude yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  12,65,"Nde Й“e udditunoo doЕ‹lle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e tawi coggeeli(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ruttaama e maЙ“Й“e. ЖЃe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko men Й—aЙ“Й“ata [kadi]? ЖЉii ko coggeeli amen, Й—i ruttaama e amen. MeЙ—en jiggana yimЙ“e amen, men reena musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“eydora Й“etu ngelooba; Й—um ko Й“etu newiingu"
  12,66,"O maaki: \"Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e mooЙ—on haa Жґettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara on huЙ“inda\". ЖЃaawo Й“e Жґettanii mo ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, o maaki: \"Alla e dow ko wowluЙ—en kon, ko O deeno"
  12,67,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e am, wata on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame seertuЙ—e. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muyЙ—e) Alla hay e huunde. Г‘aawoore alanaa si wanaa Alla: Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,68,"Nde Й“e naatirnoo nokku ka ben maЙ“Й“e yamirnoo Й“e Й—on, Й—um wonaano no duncana Й“e [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunooЙ—o e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. Kanko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal Men anndini mo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e anndaa"
  12,69,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o maЙ“Й“i neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: \"Ko mi neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko Й“e huuwaynoo"
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo Й“e doЕ‹lle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o waЙ—i etirgal ngal ka doЕ‹ngal neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotooЙ—o eewnii: \"Ko onon yo seteeЙ“e, Ko on wuyЙ“e"
  12,71,"ЖЃe fewtiti e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wi'i: \"Ko honЙ—um hattiЙ—on"
  12,72,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"Men hattike etirde laamЙ—o on. Hino woodani kala adduЙ—o ngal, doЕ‹ngal ngelooba, ko min woni fawtiiЙ—o Й—um"
  12,73,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, gomЙ—ii hiЙ—on anndi men araali bonnugol ka leydi, men laataaki kadi wuyЙ“e"
  12,74,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"Ko wonata njoЙ“di makko si tawii ko on fenooЙ“e"
  12,75,"ЖЃe wi'i: \"NjoЙ“di makko: ko kala mo: [Й—um] tawaa ka doЕ‹ngal mun, haray ko kanko [tigir] woni njoЙ“di mun. Ko wano non men yoЙ“itirta tooГ±ooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fuЙ—Й—ori doЕ‹le maЙ“Й“e Й—en ado doЕ‹ngal neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doЕ‹ngal neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laamЙ—o on, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi. MeЙ—en Й“antana darajaaji on mo Men muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]"